00:30:20.400 --> 00:30:22.000
na dati ay nag-empleyo
ng maraming manggagawa

00:30:22.000 --> 00:30:23.040
pero ngayon ay nagsara na,

00:30:23.040 --> 00:30:24.730
na nagreresulta sa malawakang kawalan ng trabaho.

00:30:24.730 --> 00:30:26.640
Hindi man lang natin dapat hayaang masyadong maraming tao

00:30:26.640 --> 00:30:27.480
magutom.

00:30:28.900 --> 00:30:30.030
At naniniwala ako

00:30:30.330 --> 00:30:32.790
basta't matatag tayong nakaugat
sa Macau,

00:30:32.860 --> 00:30:34.120
pagbabahagi ng hininga nito

00:30:34.150 --> 00:30:35.870
at tadhana,

00:30:36.640 --> 00:30:37.710
Ang kinabukasan ng Macau

00:30:37.980 --> 00:30:39.710
tiyak na makakamit ang bagong kaluwalhatian.

